From rubenfcasal en gmail.com  Wed Nov  5 16:27:49 2014
From: rubenfcasal en gmail.com (rubenfcasal)
Date: Wed, 05 Nov 2014 16:27:49 +0100
Subject: [R-es] Agregar ruido a una serie de tiempo
